snippet.title: My First Quantum Translocator - Official Walkthrough
snippet.description:
This is the official video walkthrough for My First Quantum Translocator.

Developed by Cellar Door Games:
http://www.cellardoorgames.com

Play the game at Newgrounds.com:
http://www.newgrounds.com/portal/view/548371

Music by Tettix:
http://www.tettix.net

WARNING:  The codes below show you how to unlock all the secret characters in the game.  Read at your own risk!

****

At the title screen, press the following keys at the same time.

G + L = Spacegirl
C + T = Grasshopper
N + G = Red Castle Crasher Knight
SHIFT + / (?) = The Behemoth Chicken
C + G = Perpetual Pinwheel (unlisted)
